outputs.output_descr:
Preparatory assistance for medium-sized project designed to:

a) remove barriers to Palau's efforts to reduce greenhouse gas emissions through widespread use of feasible renewable energy technologies (RETs) in rural areas;

b) widen scope of EU-funded energy development project and other foreign-assisted and government-funded projects under Palau's current energy program;

c) establishes a national policy and program for renewable energy within the context of a national energy policy, creates a conducive environment for investments in RETs for power generation at the utility level, encourages application of household and village level RET applications in areas not serviced by grid and sustain an industry to support RE technology development and commercialization.
